♪ <i>Bury your doubts… </i>♪

1721
01:34:07.833 --> 01:34:09.291
[Agnès] No! Please!

1722
01:34:09.375 --> 01:34:11.750
-Please. my son is here!
-Don't shoot. there's a kid!

1723
01:34:11.833 --> 01:34:14.291
-Put your guns down!
-We won't hurt anyone. Go. Go!

1724
01:34:14.375 --> 01:34:16.666
